groupy.gp_3x_counter 

   1from tqdm import tqdm
   2from rdkit import Chem
   3import pandas as pd
   4from joblib import Parallel, delayed
   5
   6from groupy.gp_3x_loader import Loader
   7
   8
   9# tool
  10def has_non_aromatic_neighbor(atom):
  11    """判断原子周围是否有非芳香原子"""
  12    flag = False
  13    neighbors = atom.GetNeighbors()
  14    for i in neighbors:
  15        if not i.GetIsAromatic():
  16            flag = True
  17            break
  18    return flag
  19
  20
  21def find_ring_atoms(mol, atom_idxs):
  22    """找出给定的原子索引元组中在环上的原子索引，并返回一个元组"""
  23    return list((i for i in atom_idxs if mol.GetAtomWithIdx(i).IsInRing()))
  24
  25
  26def is_in_same_ring(mol, atom_idxs: tuple):
  27    """判断一个元组中的原子索引是否在同一个环上"""
  28    flag = False
  29    all_rings = [list(i) for i in Chem.GetSymmSSSR(mol)]
  30    # set(i).issubset(j)
  31    for i in all_rings:
  32        if set(atom_idxs).issubset(i):
  33            flag = True
  34            break
  35    return flag
  36
  37
  38# f order
  39def f_001(mol):
  40    """CH3"""
  41    query = Chem.MolFromSmarts('[C;H3;!R]')
  42    match_list = mol.GetSubstructMatches(query)
  43    return len(match_list), match_list
  44
  45

  49    match_list = mol.GetSubstructMatches(query)
  50    return len(match_list), match_list

 109def f_011(mol):

 115
 116def f_012(mol):
 117    """C=C=C
 118    2001年的论文12号基团是CH=C=CH,对应的SMART为[C;H1;!R;D2]=[C;H0;!R;D2]=[C;H1;!R;D2]
 119    """
 120    query = Chem.MolFromSmarts('[C;H0;!R]=[C;H0;!R;D2]=[C;H0;!R]')
 121    match_list = mol.GetSubstructMatches(query)
 122    return len(match_list), match_list
 123

 129    return len(match_list), match_list

 139def f_015(mol):

 145
 146def f_016(mol):  # 麻烦且慢，但是应该可靠
 147    """aC fused with aromatic ring"""
 148    query = Chem.MolFromSmarts('[c;H0;R&!R1;D3]')
 149    match_list = mol.GetSubstructMatches(query)
 150    real_match_list = []
 151    for i in match_list:
 152        atom_i = mol.GetAtomWithIdx(i[0])
 153        if not has_non_aromatic_neighbor(atom_i):  # 判断该原子是否有链接非芳香原子是为了防止把芳环上连接非芳香环也算进去
 154            real_match_list.append(i)
 155    return len(real_match_list), tuple(real_match_list)
 156
 157
 158def f_017(mol):  # 麻烦且慢，但是应该可靠
 159    """aC fused with nonaromatic subring"""
 160    query = Chem.MolFromSmarts('[c;H0;R&!R1;D3]')
 161    match_list = mol.GetSubstructMatches(query)
 162    real_match_list = []
 163    for i in match_list:
 164        atom_i = mol.GetAtomWithIdx(i[0])
 165        if has_non_aromatic_neighbor(atom_i):  # 判断该原子是否有链接非芳香原子是为了取出芳环上连接非芳香环的，和上一个函数刚好相反
 166            real_match_list.append(i)
 167    return len(real_match_list), tuple(real_match_list)
 168
 169
 170def f_018(mol):
 171    """aC except as above
 172    这里这样写是因为我们给出了数基团的顺序，在那里会剔除重复的，所以不用担心重复
 173    """
 174    query = Chem.MolFromSmarts('[c;H0;R;D3]')
 175    match_list = mol.GetSubstructMatches(query)
 176    return len(match_list), match_list

2539    match_list = ()
2540    for i in range(3, len(not_in_ring_atoms) + 1):
2541        query = Chem.MolFromSmarts(
2542            '[C;H0;!R;D3](=[O;H0;!R;D1])(-[O;H1;!R;D1]){}-[C;H0;!R;D3](=[O;H0;!R;D1])(-[O;H1;!R;D1])'.format(
2543                '-[C;H0,H1,H2;!R]' * i))
2544        match_list += mol.GetSubstructMatches(query)
2545    return len(match_list), match_list

3078    match_list = mol.GetSubstructMatches(query)
3079    return len(match_list), match_list

3082def t_069(mol):
3083    """Ncyc-(CH2)3-Ncyc(different rings)"""
3084    query = Chem.MolFromSmarts('[N;H0;R;D3]!@&-[C;H2][C;H2][C;H2]!@&-[N;H0;R;D3]')
3085    match_list = mol.GetSubstructMatches(query)
3086    return len(match_list), match_list

3232    def count_a_mol(self, mol, clear_mode=False, add_note=False, add_smiles=False):
3233        init_smi = mol
3234        try:
3235            if isinstance(mol, str):
3236                mol = Chem.MolFromSmiles(mol)
3237            self.result = self.init_result.copy()
3238            if add_note:
3239                # self.result['note'] = ''
3240                self.result['note'] = Chem.MolToSmiles(mol)
3241            if add_smiles:
3242                self.result['smiles'] = Chem.MolToSmiles(mol)
3243            self.count_1st_order_groups(mol=mol, add_note=add_note)
3244            self.count_2nd_order_groups(mol=mol)
3245            self.count_3rd_order_groups(mol=mol)
3246            if clear_mode:
3247                # 清爽模式,不显示没有统计到的基团
3248                self.result = {k: v for k, v in self.result.items() if v}
3249            return self.result
3250        except:
3251            print(f'Error! There is something wrong when counting {init_smi}, please check it.')
3252            return self.init_result.copy()
3253
3254    def count_mols(self, smiles_file_path, count_result_file_path='count_result.csv', add_note=False, add_smiles=False):  # todo mpi 并行？
3255        print('reading the input file...')
3256        if smiles_file_path.endswith('.txt'):
3257            smiles_iterator = list(open(smiles_file_path))
3258        elif smiles_file_path.endswith('.xlsx'):
3259            smiles_iterator = pd.read_excel(smiles_file_path)['smiles']
3260        elif smiles_file_path.endswith('.csv'):
3261            smiles_iterator = pd.read_csv(smiles_file_path)['smiles']
3262        else:
3263            raise NotImplementedError(
3264                'ERROR: The file type cannot be read, use the.txt/.xlsx/.csv file as the input file.')
3265
3266        mol_number = len(smiles_iterator)
3267        print('Done, totally detected {} molecules, start counting...'.format(mol_number))
3268        count_result_dict_list = []
3269        for i in tqdm(smiles_iterator):
3270            count_result_dict_list.append(self.count_a_mol(i, add_note=add_note, add_smiles=add_smiles))
3271        print('Done!')
3272        print('writing to csv...')
3273        result = pd.DataFrame(count_result_dict_list)
3274        result.to_csv(count_result_file_path, index_label='index')
3275        print('Done!')
3276        return result
3277
3278    def count_mols_mpi(self, smiles_file_path, count_result_file_path='count_result.csv', add_note=False, add_smiles=False, n_jobs=1, batch_size='auto'):
3279        print('reading the input file...')
3280        if smiles_file_path.endswith('.txt'):
3281            smiles_iterator = list(open(smiles_file_path))
3282        elif smiles_file_path.endswith('.xlsx'):
3283            smiles_iterator = pd.read_excel(smiles_file_path)['smiles']
3284        elif smiles_file_path.endswith('.csv'):
3285            smiles_iterator = pd.read_csv(smiles_file_path)['smiles']
3286        else:
3287            raise NotImplementedError(
3288                'ERROR: The file type cannot be read, use the.txt/.xlsx/.csv file as the input file.')
3289
3290        mol_number = len(smiles_iterator)
3291        print('Done, totally detected {} molecules, start counting...'.format(mol_number))
3292        task = [delayed(self.count_a_mol)(i, add_note=add_note, add_smiles=add_smiles) for i in smiles_iterator]
3293        count_result_dict_list = Parallel(n_jobs=n_jobs, batch_size=batch_size)(task)
3294        print('Done!')
3295        print('writing to csv...')
3296        result = pd.DataFrame(count_result_dict_list)
3297        result.to_csv(count_result_file_path, index_label='index')
3298        print('Done!')
3299        return result
3300
3301    def get_group_fingerprint(self, mol):
3302        count_result = self.count_a_mol(mol=mol, clear_mode=False, add_note=False)
3303        return [value for key, value in count_result.items()]
3304
3305    def count_1st_order_groups(self, mol, add_note=False):
3306        atoms_index = set([i for i in range(len(mol.GetAtoms()))])  # 所有原子序号的集合
3307        used_atoms_index = set()
3308        for function_index in self.f_order_group_function_order:
3309            function = self.f_order_group_function[function_index]
3310            _, tuple_of_match_tuples = function(mol)
3311            for matched_index in tuple_of_match_tuples:
3312                if used_atoms_index.intersection(matched_index) == set():
3313                    used_atoms_index = used_atoms_index.union(matched_index)
3314                    self.result[function.__name__] += 1
3315            if used_atoms_index == atoms_index:
3316                # early stop 统计第一顺序基团时，当所有原子都被使用后提前停止
3317                break
3318
3319        if used_atoms_index != atoms_index:
3320            warning = 'WARING: For {}, The first order groups do not cover the whole molecule! The results may not be reliable!'.format(
3321                Chem.MolToSmiles(mol))
3322            print(warning)
3323            if add_note:
3324                if self.result.get('note', 0):
3325                    self.result['note'] += '\t'
3326                    self.result['note'] += warning
3327                else:
3328                    self.result['note'] = warning
3329        return None
3330
3331    def count_2nd_order_groups(self, mol):
3332        s_order_group_in_mol = []
3333        for function_index in self.s_order_group_function_order:
3334            function = self.s_order_group_function[function_index]
3335            _, tuple_of_match_tuples = function(mol)
3336            for matched_index in tuple_of_match_tuples:
3337                matched_index = set(matched_index)
3338                for used in s_order_group_in_mol:  # for else 语句
3339                    if matched_index.issubset(used):
3340                        break
3341                else:
3342                    s_order_group_in_mol.append(matched_index)
3343                    self.result[function.__name__] += 1
3344        return None
3345
3346    def count_3rd_order_groups(self, mol):  # 跟count_2nd_order_groups几乎完全一样
3347        t_order_group_in_mol = []
3348        for function_index in self.t_order_group_function_order:
3349            function = self.t_order_group_function[function_index]
3350            _, tuple_of_match_tuples = function(mol)
3351            for matched_index in tuple_of_match_tuples:
3352                matched_index = set(matched_index)
3353                for used in t_order_group_in_mol:  # for else 语句
3354                    if matched_index.issubset(used):
3355                        break
3356                else:
3357                    t_order_group_in_mol.append(matched_index)
3358                    self.result[function.__name__] += 1
3359        return None
3360
3361

def has_non_aromatic_neighbor(atom): 
11def has_non_aromatic_neighbor(atom):
12    """判断原子周围是否有非芳香原子"""
13    flag = False
14    neighbors = atom.GetNeighbors()
15    for i in neighbors:
16        if not i.GetIsAromatic():
17            flag = True
18            break
19    return flag

判断原子周围是否有非芳香原子

def find_ring_atoms(mol, atom_idxs): 
22def find_ring_atoms(mol, atom_idxs):
23    """找出给定的原子索引元组中在环上的原子索引，并返回一个元组"""
24    return list((i for i in atom_idxs if mol.GetAtomWithIdx(i).IsInRing()))

找出给定的原子索引元组中在环上的原子索引，并返回一个元组

def is_in_same_ring(mol, atom_idxs: tuple): 
27def is_in_same_ring(mol, atom_idxs: tuple):
28    """判断一个元组中的原子索引是否在同一个环上"""
29    flag = False
30    all_rings = [list(i) for i in Chem.GetSymmSSSR(mol)]
31    # set(i).issubset(j)
32    for i in all_rings:
33        if set(atom_idxs).issubset(i):
34            flag = True
35            break
36    return flag

判断一个元组中的原子索引是否在同一个环上

def f_016(mol): 
147def f_016(mol):  # 麻烦且慢，但是应该可靠
148    """aC fused with aromatic ring"""
149    query = Chem.MolFromSmarts('[c;H0;R&!R1;D3]')
150    match_list = mol.GetSubstructMatches(query)
151    real_match_list = []
152    for i in match_list:
153        atom_i = mol.GetAtomWithIdx(i[0])
154        if not has_non_aromatic_neighbor(atom_i):  # 判断该原子是否有链接非芳香原子是为了防止把芳环上连接非芳香环也算进去
155            real_match_list.append(i)
156    return len(real_match_list), tuple(real_match_list)

aC fused with aromatic ring

def f_017(mol): 
159def f_017(mol):  # 麻烦且慢，但是应该可靠
160    """aC fused with nonaromatic subring"""
161    query = Chem.MolFromSmarts('[c;H0;R&!R1;D3]')
162    match_list = mol.GetSubstructMatches(query)
163    real_match_list = []
164    for i in match_list:
165        atom_i = mol.GetAtomWithIdx(i[0])
166        if has_non_aromatic_neighbor(atom_i):  # 判断该原子是否有链接非芳香原子是为了取出芳环上连接非芳香环的，和上一个函数刚好相反
167            real_match_list.append(i)
168    return len(real_match_list), tuple(real_match_list)

aC fused with nonaromatic subring

3233    def count_a_mol(self, mol, clear_mode=False, add_note=False, add_smiles=False):
3234        init_smi = mol
3235        try:
3236            if isinstance(mol, str):
3237                mol = Chem.MolFromSmiles(mol)
3238            self.result = self.init_result.copy()
3239            if add_note:
3240                # self.result['note'] = ''
3241                self.result['note'] = Chem.MolToSmiles(mol)
3242            if add_smiles:
3243                self.result['smiles'] = Chem.MolToSmiles(mol)
3244            self.count_1st_order_groups(mol=mol, add_note=add_note)
3245            self.count_2nd_order_groups(mol=mol)
3246            self.count_3rd_order_groups(mol=mol)
3247            if clear_mode:
3248                # 清爽模式,不显示没有统计到的基团
3249                self.result = {k: v for k, v in self.result.items() if v}
3250            return self.result
3251        except:
3252            print(f'Error! There is something wrong when counting {init_smi}, please check it.')
3253            return self.init_result.copy()
3254
3255    def count_mols(self, smiles_file_path, count_result_file_path='count_result.csv', add_note=False, add_smiles=False):  # todo mpi 并行？
3256        print('reading the input file...')
3257        if smiles_file_path.endswith('.txt'):
3258            smiles_iterator = list(open(smiles_file_path))
3259        elif smiles_file_path.endswith('.xlsx'):
3260            smiles_iterator = pd.read_excel(smiles_file_path)['smiles']
3261        elif smiles_file_path.endswith('.csv'):
3262            smiles_iterator = pd.read_csv(smiles_file_path)['smiles']
3263        else:
3264            raise NotImplementedError(
3265                'ERROR: The file type cannot be read, use the.txt/.xlsx/.csv file as the input file.')
3266
3267        mol_number = len(smiles_iterator)
3268        print('Done, totally detected {} molecules, start counting...'.format(mol_number))
3269        count_result_dict_list = []
3270        for i in tqdm(smiles_iterator):
3271            count_result_dict_list.append(self.count_a_mol(i, add_note=add_note, add_smiles=add_smiles))
3272        print('Done!')
3273        print('writing to csv...')
3274        result = pd.DataFrame(count_result_dict_list)
3275        result.to_csv(count_result_file_path, index_label='index')
3276        print('Done!')
3277        return result
3278
3279    def count_mols_mpi(self, smiles_file_path, count_result_file_path='count_result.csv', add_note=False, add_smiles=False, n_jobs=1, batch_size='auto'):
3280        print('reading the input file...')
3281        if smiles_file_path.endswith('.txt'):
3282            smiles_iterator = list(open(smiles_file_path))
3283        elif smiles_file_path.endswith('.xlsx'):
3284            smiles_iterator = pd.read_excel(smiles_file_path)['smiles']
3285        elif smiles_file_path.endswith('.csv'):
3286            smiles_iterator = pd.read_csv(smiles_file_path)['smiles']
3287        else:
3288            raise NotImplementedError(
3289                'ERROR: The file type cannot be read, use the.txt/.xlsx/.csv file as the input file.')
3290
3291        mol_number = len(smiles_iterator)
3292        print('Done, totally detected {} molecules, start counting...'.format(mol_number))
3293        task = [delayed(self.count_a_mol)(i, add_note=add_note, add_smiles=add_smiles) for i in smiles_iterator]
3294        count_result_dict_list = Parallel(n_jobs=n_jobs, batch_size=batch_size)(task)
3295        print('Done!')
3296        print('writing to csv...')
3297        result = pd.DataFrame(count_result_dict_list)
3298        result.to_csv(count_result_file_path, index_label='index')
3299        print('Done!')
3300        return result
3301
3302    def get_group_fingerprint(self, mol):
3303        count_result = self.count_a_mol(mol=mol, clear_mode=False, add_note=False)
3304        return [value for key, value in count_result.items()]
3305
3306    def count_1st_order_groups(self, mol, add_note=False):
3307        atoms_index = set([i for i in range(len(mol.GetAtoms()))])  # 所有原子序号的集合
3308        used_atoms_index = set()
3309        for function_index in self.f_order_group_function_order:
3310            function = self.f_order_group_function[function_index]
3311            _, tuple_of_match_tuples = function(mol)
3312            for matched_index in tuple_of_match_tuples:
3313                if used_atoms_index.intersection(matched_index) == set():
3314                    used_atoms_index = used_atoms_index.union(matched_index)
3315                    self.result[function.__name__] += 1
3316            if used_atoms_index == atoms_index:
3317                # early stop 统计第一顺序基团时，当所有原子都被使用后提前停止
3318                break
3319
3320        if used_atoms_index != atoms_index:
3321            warning = 'WARING: For {}, The first order groups do not cover the whole molecule! The results may not be reliable!'.format(
3322                Chem.MolToSmiles(mol))
3323            print(warning)
3324            if add_note:
3325                if self.result.get('note', 0):
3326                    self.result['note'] += '\t'
3327                    self.result['note'] += warning
3328                else:
3329                    self.result['note'] = warning
3330        return None
3331
3332    def count_2nd_order_groups(self, mol):
3333        s_order_group_in_mol = []
3334        for function_index in self.s_order_group_function_order:
3335            function = self.s_order_group_function[function_index]
3336            _, tuple_of_match_tuples = function(mol)
3337            for matched_index in tuple_of_match_tuples:
3338                matched_index = set(matched_index)
3339                for used in s_order_group_in_mol:  # for else 语句
3340                    if matched_index.issubset(used):
3341                        break
3342                else:
3343                    s_order_group_in_mol.append(matched_index)
3344                    self.result[function.__name__] += 1
3345        return None
3346
3347    def count_3rd_order_groups(self, mol):  # 跟count_2nd_order_groups几乎完全一样
3348        t_order_group_in_mol = []
3349        for function_index in self.t_order_group_function_order:
3350            function = self.t_order_group_function[function_index]
3351            _, tuple_of_match_tuples = function(mol)
3352            for matched_index in tuple_of_match_tuples:
3353                matched_index = set(matched_index)
3354                for used in t_order_group_in_mol:  # for else 语句
3355                    if matched_index.issubset(used):
3356                        break
3357                else:
3358                    t_order_group_in_mol.append(matched_index)
3359                    self.result[function.__name__] += 1
3360        return None
